alerts.description:
There is a risk of persistent rain (Level 2 of 4).
Precipitation amounts: 50-80 l/m²; in windward areas: < 100 l/m²

There is a risk of hurricane-force gusts (Level 3 of 4).
Height range: > 1000 m; Max. gusts: 105-130 km/h; Wind direction: south-west then west

There is a risk of gale-force gusts (Level 2 of 4).
Max. gusts: 55-70 km/h; Wind direction: west; Increased gusts: in exposed locations < 80 km/h

There is a risk of storm-force gusts (Level 2 of 4).
Height range: > 800 m; Max. gusts: 80-100 km/h; Wind direction: west

There is a risk of gale-force gusts (Level 2 of 4).
Max. gusts: 65-75 km/h; Wind direction: west; Increased gusts: in exposed locations < 90 km/h

There is a risk of wind gusts (level 1 of 4).
Max. gusts: ~ 55 km/h; Wind direction: west; Increased gusts: in exposed locations < 70 km/h
